{"tid":931268,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[彈出彈入]聯儲局據報正考慮減慢加息步伐","createTime":"2018-12-07T02:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T04:20:11.000Z","uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"329d8a2790915cb3791b9b54660927916191d7d1","tid":931268,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:08:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=329894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D329894&d=RGtujUXDJSHD%2FDnQ12ZO01eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=30b5e832\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D329894&h=7b17273e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=329894</a><br />\n【Now新聞台】美國聯儲局據報正考慮於未來加息上採取觀望態度，可能減慢加息步伐。<br />\n<br />\n聯儲局將於本月18至19日舉行今年最後1次議息，外界普遍預料這次會議很大機會宣布加息。《華爾街日報》報道，聯儲局官員正考慮這次會議後應否向市場示意，由目前漸進加息策略改為採取觀望態度，未來的加息決定將根據議息前幾周的經濟數據和市場表現而定，意味未來加息步伐可能減慢。<br />\n<br />\n若果沿用現時的做法，聯儲局12月加息後，下一次加息將會是明年3月，但聯儲局官員對12月後下次加息時間仍然不確定，因為美國通脹近幾個月回軟，連同油價進一步下跌，降低聯儲局每季加息的迫切性。<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母, 侵侵就做short, 你條撚樣就做long.<br />\n彈上彈落幾百點咁黎, 玩撚啦"},{"pid":"50d136dade93529ded45e6ec77e9f42b47c31288","tid":931268,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:12:13.000Z","msg":"屌 佢玩哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74f066158211e0c81a8cccc7efc30f30572e004","tid":931268,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"留名睇低智仔打J"},{"pid":"d9301bd73025859d9b42796d9baef230e9a792ac","tid":931268,"uid":215202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T02:14:45.000Z","msg":"聯儲局成日同侵侵唱反調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cc0c8633b9d3386ad0ef5e3952063c97990bf1","tid":931268,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12